## install

```
# make sure you have install cmake libssl-dev (on linux)
pip install je_auto_control
```

## Info

* requirement
    * Python 3.7 & later
    * pip 19.3 & later


* Dev env
    * windows 11
    * osx 11 big sur
    * ubuntu 20.0.4


* Test on
    * windows 10 ~ 11
    * osx 10.5 ~ 11 big sur
    * ubuntu 20.0.4
    * raspberry pi 3B and 4B
